{"id":13520,"date":"2022-06-23T16:25:56","date_gmt":"2022-06-23T09:25:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=13520"},"modified":"2022-06-23T16:25:57","modified_gmt":"2022-06-23T09:25:57","slug":"lai-hyundai-santa-fe-co-thuc-su-an-toan","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/lai-hyundai-santa-fe-co-thuc-su-an-toan\/","title":{"rendered":"L\u00c1I HYUNDAI SANTA FE C\u00d3 TH\u1ef0C S\u1ef0 AN TO\u00c0N?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong>Hyundai SantaFe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng an to\u00e0n 5 sao cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb C\u1ee5c an to\u00e0n giao th\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c gia M\u1ef9 (NHTSA). Vi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m an to\u00e0n xa l\u1ed9 M\u1ef9 (IIHS) c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn Santa Fe \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Top Safety Pick+ v\u00e0 m\u1eabu SUV c\u1ee1 trung c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt m\u1edbi v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eb7t s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng l\u00e0m \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/lai-hyundai-santa-fe-co-thuc-su-an-toan\/6e6f982f-6eb7-442e-81f1-fdfb7415ea12\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13526\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-13526\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/6e6f982f-6eb7-442e-81f1-fdfb7415ea12-1024x667.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"417\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/6e6f982f-6eb7-442e-81f1-fdfb7415ea12-1024x667.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/6e6f982f-6eb7-442e-81f1-fdfb7415ea12-300x195.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/6e6f982f-6eb7-442e-81f1-fdfb7415ea12-768x500.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/6e6f982f-6eb7-442e-81f1-fdfb7415ea12.jpg 1332w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>Santafe \u0111\u00e3 \u01b0u \u00e1i trang b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng an to\u00e0n cho xe. Ngo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng trang b\u1ecb an to\u00e0n chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c nh\u01b0:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3 c\u1ee9ng phanh \u2013 ABS<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed \u2013 ESC<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 phanh kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p \u2013 BA<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/lai-hyundai-santa-fe-co-thuc-su-an-toan\/a39a06ee-c0ef-4148-a686-c6745ce05517\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13528\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-13528\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/a39a06ee-c0ef-4148-a686-c6745ce05517-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/a39a06ee-c0ef-4148-a686-c6745ce05517-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/a39a06ee-c0ef-4148-a686-c6745ce05517-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/a39a06ee-c0ef-4148-a686-c6745ce05517-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/a39a06ee-c0ef-4148-a686-c6745ce05517.jpg 1157w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 xu\u1ed1ng d\u1ed1c \u2013 DBC<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i l\u1ef1c phanh \u2013 EBD<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ch\u1ed1ng tr\u01b0\u1ee3t th\u00e2n xe \u2013 VSM<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh ngang d\u1ed1c \u2013 HAC<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1eef l\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng &#8211; lKA<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/lai-hyundai-santa-fe-co-thuc-su-an-toan\/29a179e7-3348-4e4f-9813-2cd9f034a7c6\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13530\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-13530\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29a179e7-3348-4e4f-9813-2cd9f034a7c6-1024x833.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"521\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29a179e7-3348-4e4f-9813-2cd9f034a7c6-1024x833.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29a179e7-3348-4e4f-9813-2cd9f034a7c6-300x244.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29a179e7-3348-4e4f-9813-2cd9f034a7c6-768x625.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29a179e7-3348-4e4f-9813-2cd9f034a7c6.jpg 1067w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>6 t\u00fai kh\u00ed<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Ngo\u00e0i ra, Santafe 2021 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng an to\u00e0n th\u00f4ng minh h\u01a1n nh\u01b0:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>C\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o l\u00f9i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n c\u1eaft ngang RCCA<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/lai-hyundai-santa-fe-co-thuc-su-an-toan\/2ebb4e67-7f3f-4415-b80b-01c07d25e306\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13527\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13527\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/2ebb4e67-7f3f-4415-b80b-01c07d25e306.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/2ebb4e67-7f3f-4415-b80b-01c07d25e306.jpg 925w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/2ebb4e67-7f3f-4415-b80b-01c07d25e306-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/2ebb4e67-7f3f-4415-b80b-01c07d25e306-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/2ebb4e67-7f3f-4415-b80b-01c07d25e306-768x768.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Kh\u00f3a an to\u00e0n th\u00f4ng minh SAE<\/li>\n<li>C\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i b\u1ed9<\/li>\n<li>Phanh tay \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed EPB<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t &amp; ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh va ch\u1ea1m \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00f9 BVM &amp; BCA<\/li>\n<li>G\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ed1ng ch\u00f3i t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng ECM<\/li>\n<li>T\u00edch h\u1ee3p la b\u00e0n gi\u1eef phanh t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng Auto Hold<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed7 xe PDW<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a m\u00e3 h\u00f3a &amp; h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ed9m Immobilizer.<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u00e8n pha th\u00edch \u1ee9ng Adaptive High Beam AHB<\/li>\n<li>Kh\u00f3a tr\u1ebb em an to\u00e0n SEA<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/lai-hyundai-santa-fe-co-thuc-su-an-toan\/3-8\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13522\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13522\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/3.png 900w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/3-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/3-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/3-768x768.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Hyundai SantaFe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng an to\u00e0n 5 sao cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb C\u1ee5c an to\u00e0n giao th\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c gia M\u1ef9 (NHTSA). Vi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m an to\u00e0n xa l\u1ed9 M\u1ef9 (IIHS) c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn Santa Fe \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Top Safe